<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="pride-n">pride <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /praɪd/    美 /praɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>自豪；骄傲：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>a sense of</strong> national <strong>pride</strong>
民族自豪感</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was filled with pride. 
我满怀自豪。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>引起自豪的人 / 事物：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I think he is <strong>the pride of</strong> our Chinese people.
我认为他是我们中国人的骄傲。</p><footer>北师大⑥ – 16</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>sb’s pride and joy
使某人感到骄傲和快乐的人 / 事物</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>自尊；尊严：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His pride prevents him from doing anything dishonourable.
他的自尊使他不会做出任何不光彩的事情。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>自负；傲慢：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Pride goes before a fall.
骄兵必败。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="take-pride-in">take pride in</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对…感到自豪：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People tend to take pride in keeping everything in their street fresh.
人们往往会为保持自己的街道清爽而感到自豪。</p><footer>2018 浙江</footer></div>

<h3 id="with-pride">with pride</h3>
<p>1.<strong>自豪地：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I looked with pride at what I had achieved. 
回顾过去的成就，我感到很自豪。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>Rebecca was the <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (骄傲) of her family.  （2012 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. pride  </p></div>